data.chText: （用以比较或对比两个事实）然而，但是，尽管
data.enText: used to compare or contrast two facts

data.chText: 有一些研究结果令人满意，然而其他的则不然。
data.enText: Some of the studies show positive results, whereas others do not.

data.chText: （用于正式文件中句子的开头）鉴于
data.enText: used at the beginning of a sentence in an official document to mean ‘because of the fact that…’

means: (用以比较或对比两个事实)然而，但是，尽管
(用于正式文件中句子的开头)鉴于

value.def: You use whereas to introduce a comment which contrasts with what is said in the main clause.

example.ex: Pensions are linked to inflation, whereas they should be linked to the cost of living...
example.tran: 养老金与通货膨胀挂钩，然而它们其实应该和生活费用挂钩。

example.ex: Whereas the population of working age increased by 1 million between 1981 and 1986, today it is barely growing.
example.tran: 1981年到1986年间适龄工作人口增长了100万，而现如今该人口数却几乎没有增长。
